{"word":"Self-Will","slug":"self-will","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Self-Will</b> Stubbornness.<br/> Forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=30&verse=8'>2Ch 30:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=75&verse=5'>Psa 75:5</a><br/> Proceeds from:<br/> - Unbelief<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=14'>2Ki 17:14</a> <br/> - Pride<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=16'>Neh 9:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=29'>Neh 9:29</a> <br/> - An evil heart<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=24'>Jer 7:24</a> <br/> God knows<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=48&verse=4'>Isa 48:4</a><br/> Exhibited in:<br/> - Exhibited in:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=1&verse=24'>Pro 1:24</a> <br/> - Refusing to hearken to the messengers of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=19'>1Sa 8:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=44&verse=16'>Jer 44:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=7&verse=11'>Zec 7:11</a> <br/> - Refusing to walk in the ways of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=17'>Neh 9:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=42&verse=24'>Isa 42:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=10'>Psa 78:10</a> <br/> - Refusing to hearken to parents<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=19'>Deu 21:19</a> <br/> - Refusing to receive correction<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=18'>Deu 21:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=5&verse=3'>Jer 5:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=28'>Jer 7:28</a> <br/> - Rebelling against God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=27'>Deu 31:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=8'>Psa 78:8</a> <br/> - Resisting the Holy Ghost<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=51'>Act 7:51</a> <br/> - Walking in the counsels of an evil heart<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=24'>Jer 7:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=23&verse=17'>Jer 23:17</a> <br/> - Hardening the neck<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=16'>Neh 9:16</a> <br/> - Hardening the heart<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=13'>2Ch 36:13</a> <br/> - Going backward and not forward<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=24'>Jer 7:24</a> <br/> - Heinousness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=15&verse=23'>1Sa 15:23</a> <br/> Ministers should:<br/> - Be without<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=1&verse=7'>Tit 1:7</a> <br/> - Warn their people against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=3&verse=12'>Heb 3:12</a> <br/> - Pray that their people may be forgiven for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=9'>Exo 34:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=27'>Deu 9:27</a> <br/> Characteristic of the wicked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=7&verse=11'>Pro 7:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=10'>2Pe 2:10</a><br/> The wicked cease not from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=2&verse=19'>Jdg 2:19</a><br/> Punishment for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=21'>Deu 21:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=29&verse=1